<% content_for :title, "About - Lost Pets Registry" %>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 shadow-lg rounded-lg p-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-6">About Lost Pets Registry</h1>

    <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6 text-lg">
        Lost Pets Registry is a platform dedicated to helping reunite lost pets with their families.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        Every year, millions of pets go missing. Our mission is to provide a free, easy-to-use platform where pet owners can report lost animals and community members can report found pets, helping to bring families back together.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Report a lost pet</strong> - Create a detailed listing with photos and last known location</li>
        <li><strong>Report a found pet</strong> - Help a lost pet find its way home by posting sighting information</li>
        <li><strong>Search listings</strong> - Browse reported pets in your area</li>
        <li><strong>Connect with others</strong> - Message other users about potential matches</li>
        <li><strong>Submit tips</strong> - Share sightings and helpful information on pet listings</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">Get Involved</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        This project runs on the generosity of others. If you'd like to support our work, consider making a donation or spreading the word about our platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        Have questions or feedback? We'd love to hear from you.
        <%= link_to "Contact us", "/contact", class: "text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline" %>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
